  "texts": [
    "In this context, the motivation of our work is to provide pioneering navigation for AI practitioners and data mining projects with respect to privacy preservation.",
    "It is difficult for the general professional public to deal with or orient themselves towards two broad complementary trends in data analytics, both from a theoretical point of view and practical approaches.",
    "It is even difficult for them to select the right tools from the multitude of frameworks, libraries, and approaches available from all the ML/DL user communities in different applicable areas.",
    "Our goal is to help them overcome such difficulties comfortably in understanding AI data privacy to progress faster in the implementation of their projects or in the development of their research.",
    "The scope of this document emphasizes the importance of creating AI systems that are reliable and human-centered."
  ],
